20of%20a%20digital%20nomad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20fortunate%20to%20be%20working%20in%20a%20startup%20whose%20culture%20was%20built%20on%20remote%20working.%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20go%20out%20of%20my%20way%20to%20pitch%20it%20to%20my%20bosses%20since%20they%20supported%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20parents%20were%20a%20little%20worried%20since%20I%20would%20be%20traveling%20solo.%20But%20they%20saw%20the%20benefits%20of%20such%20an%20experience%2C%20which%20could%20help%20me%20grow%20and%20learn%20to%20be%20more%20independent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMoving%20to%20South%20Korea%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221290%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kok%20at%20Juknokwon%20Bamboo%20Garden%20at%20Damyang%2C%20South%20Korea.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b7479843bb77284ba13854%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22968%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKok%20traveled%20around%20the%20southern%20parts%20of%20South%20Korea%20while%20working%20remotely%20there.%20As%20part%20of%20her%20travels%2C%20she%20visited%20the%20Juknokwon%20Bamboo%20Garden%20in%20Damyang%20(pictured).%3Cp%3EWyin%20Kok%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20try%20out%20the%20digital%20nomad%20lifestyle%20in%20South%20Korea.%20I%20also%20traveled%20to%20Japan%20and%20Thailand%20for%20monthlong%20short%20stints%20during%20my%20year%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20making%20South%20Korea%20the%20country%20I%20spent%20most%20of%20my%20time%20in%20that%20year%20felt%20like%20a%20natural%20choice.%20Even%20before%20the%20pandemic%2C%20I%20would%20visit%20Korea%20at%20least%20once%20a%20year.%20I%20loved%20the%20country's%20cuisine%20and%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20helped%20that%20I%20had%20started%20learning%20the%20Korean%20language%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20I%20thought%20living%20there%20would%20be%20a%20good%20opportunity%20for%20me%20to%20practice%20the%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKorea's%20strong%20caf%C3%A9%20culture%20was%20also%20a%20huge%20draw%20for%20me.%20People%20usually%20study%20and%20work%20at%20caf%C3%A9s%20there%2C%20so%20I%20figured%20the%20wide%20choice%20of%20remote%20working%20spots%20was%20convenient%20for%20a%20digital%20nomad%20like%20myself.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20though%20Korea%20was%20a%20relatively%20safe%20and%20familiar%20country%20to%20me%2C%20the%20initial%20stages%20of%20living%20there%20were%20still%20nerve-racking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20solo%20female%20traveler%2C%20I%20had%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20be%20vigilant%20and%20protect%20myself.%20I%20steered%20clear%20of%20dangerous%20places%2C%20like%20dark%20back%20alleys%20and%20side%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20because%20I%20didn't%20know%20many%20people%20in%20Korea%2C%20the%20early%20days%20of%20my%20stay%20there%20felt%20lonely.%20I%20had%20to%20get%20comfortable%20with%20doing%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20on%20my%20own%2C%20whether%20having%20meals%20or%20going%20on%20grocery%20runs%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELife%20as%20a%20digital%20nomad%20made%20me%20more%20confident%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kok%20visited%20the%20Hwadamsup%20Forest%20in%20autumn%20last%20year.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b74fb5ac2de4f17ee5572c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKok%20visited%20the%20Hwadamsup%20Forest%20in%20autumn%20last%20year.%3Cp%3EWyin%20Kok%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%2C%20the%20time%20I%20spent%20as%20a%20digital%20nomad%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20enriching%20years%20of%20my%20life.%20I%20learned%20so%20much%20about%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20alone%20made%20me%20a%20lot%20more%20confident.%20I%20realized%20I%20could%20be%20strong%20and%20rely%20less%20on%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20I%20really%20enjoyed%20my%20own%20company.%20I%20no%20longer%20feel%20as%20bothered%20if%20I%20can't