ift-harris-houston-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esent%20a%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20state's%20attorney%20general%20in%20January%20asking%20him%20to%20declare%20the%20Harris%20County%20income%20plan%20unconstitutional.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBettencourt's%20request%20came%20on%20the%20same%20day%20that%20the%20program%20%E2%80%94%20called%20Uplift%20Harris%20%E2%80%94%20started%20taking%20applications.%20The%20Uplift%20Harris%20program%20plans%20to%20provide%20eligible%20households%20in%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fuplift.harriscountytx.gov%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHarris%20County%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0which%20includes%20Houston%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faustin-guarunteed-basic-income-gbi-ubi-housing-security-homeless-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24500%20a%20month%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20up%20to%2018%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECounty%20officials%20used%20more%20than%20%2420%20million%20of%20federal%20COVID-19%20relief%20from%20the%20American%20Rescue%20Plan%20to%20fund%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20program%20received%20more%20than%2076%2C000%20applicants%2C%20according%20to%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.houstonchronicle.com%2Fpolitics%2Fhouston%2Farticle%2Fdeadline-harris-county-guaranteed-income-18644380.php%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOver%252076%252C000%2520applications%2520have%2520been%2CSunnyside%252C%2520Gulfton%2520and%2520Galena%2520Park.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHouston%20Chronicle%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20applications%20for%20the%20program%20closed%20on%20Friday%2C%20Bettencourt%20appeared%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fmedia%2Ftexas-lawmaker-challenges-lottery-socialism-urges-state-ag-rule-universal-income-program%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFox%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20further%20voice%20his%20unhappiness%20with%20the%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20just%20can't%20hand%20out%20money%20l