ly%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cancer.gov%2Fnews-events%2Fcancer-currents-blog%2F2020%2Fcervical-cancer-screening-hpv-test-guideline%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Cancer%20Society%3C%2Fa%3E%20recommends%20women%20undergo%20cervical%20cancer%20screenings%20starting%20at%20age%2025.%20The%20disease%20has%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcervical-cancer-signs-symptoms-pain-vagina-discharge-blood-2022-9%23%3A~%3Atext%3DJohn%2520Butler%252C%2520a%2520consultant%2520gynecological%2Cbetween%2520periods%252C%2520or%2520after%2520menopause.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esymptoms%20that%20are%20easy%20to%20miss%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20unusual%20vaginal%20bleeding%20or%20pelvic%20pain%2C%20but%20it%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Brare%26quot%3B%20disease%20for%20women%20who%20are%20regularly%20screened%2C%20BI%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpoonam-pandey-death-hoax-cervical-cancer-awareness-stunt-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707080901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bff9a443bb77284ba35dce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpoonam-pandey-death-hoax-cervical-cancer-awareness-stunt-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Poonam%20Pandey%20says%20she%20posted%20that%20she%20died%20from%20cervical%20cancer%20to%20raise%20awareness%20for%20women%20who%20actually%20died%20from%20the%20disease.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kbalevic%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Balevic)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpoonam-pandey-death-hoax-cervical-cancer-awareness-stunt-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Watc