0the%20headquarters%20of%20tech%20giants%20Facebook%20and%20YouTube%2C%20and%20Electronic%20Arts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20wealthy%20Silicon%20Valley%20county%20in%20California%20has%20become%20the%20first%20in%20the%20US%20to%20declare%20loneliness%20a%20public%20health%20emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20as%20global%20concerns%20over%20the%20physical%20and%20mental%20impacts%20of%20isolation%20continue%20to%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Board%20of%20Supervisors%20in%20California's%20San%20Mateo%20County%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fsilicon-valley-county-loneliness-health-emergency-rcna136777%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epassed%20a%20resolution%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20included%20a%20pledge%20to%20help%20citizens%20connect%20with%20each%20other%2C%20NBC%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESan%20Mateo%20County%20is%20one%20of%20the%20wealthiest%20in%20the%20US%20and%20is%20home%20to%20the%20headquarters%20of%20many%20tech%20giants%2C%20including%20Facebook%2C%20YouTube%2C%20and%20Electronic%20Arts.%20In%20Q3%202023%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nar.realtor%2Fresearch-and-statistics%2Fhousing-statistics%2Fcounty-median-home-prices-and-monthly-mortgage-payment%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emedian%20cost%20of%20a%20home%20in%20the%20county%20was%20%241%2C573%2C470.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20San%20Mateo%20resolution%20does%20not%20provide%20any%20funding%20to%20combat%20loneliness%2C%20it%20is%20a%20sign%20of%20a%20commitment%20to%20the%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20validates%20people's%20feelings%2C%20David%20Canepa%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20Board%20of%20Supervisors%20that%20introduced%20the%20legislation%2C%20said%2C%20per%20NBC%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we're%20trying%20to%20do%20is%20to%20really%20get%20people%20out%20of%20the%20corners%20and%20say%2C%20'Hey%2C%20look%2C%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20are%20feeling%20like%20you.%20You're%20not%20alone.%20And%20moving%20forward%2C%20here%20are%20some%20of%20the%20things%20that%20we%20can%20do%20to%20support%20you%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20Surgeon%20General%20Vivek%20Murthy%20last%20year%20released%20a%20report%20on%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hhs.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fsurgeon-general-social-connection-advisory.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eepidemic%20of%20loneliness%20and%20isolation%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20report%2C%20Murthy%20said%20that%20social%20connection%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20critical%20and%20underappreciated%20contributor%20to%20individual%20and%20population%20health%2C%20community%20safety%2C%20resilience%2C%20and%20prosperity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMurthy%20said%20that%20problems%20associated%20with%20loneliness%20had%20been%20building%20for%20decades%2C%20but%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20had%20compounded%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20loneliness%20was%20%26quot%3Bassociated%20with%20a%20greater%20risk%20of%20cardiovascular%20disease%2C%20dementia%2C%20stroke%2C%20depression%2C%20anxiety%2C%20and%20premature%20death%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bmortality%20impact%20of%20being%20socially%20disconnected%20is%20similar%20to%20that%20caused%20by%20smoking%20up%20to%2015%20cigarettes%20a%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGovernments%20around%20the%20world%20have%20started%20to%20address%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fnews%2Fjoint-message-from-the-uk-and-japanese-loneliness-ministers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJapan%20and%20the%20UK%20have%20appointed%20ministers%20for%20loneliness%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20while%20New%20York%20state%20appointed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psychiatrist.com%2Fnews%2Fruth-westheimer-md-appointed-the-countrys-first-loneliness-ambassador%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNew%2520York%2520State%2520appointed%2520Dr%2C%252C%2520heart%2520disease%252C%2520and%2520stroke.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS's%20first%20honorary%20loneliness%20ambassador%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227344%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22facebook%20hq%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5bd72ae73e37946ce77edfd4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224896%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EStephen%20Lam%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20San%20Mateo%20County%2C%20Canepa%20has%20proposed%20several%20ideas%20to%20combat%20the%20problem%2C%20including%20making%20neighborhoods%20more%20walkable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20to%20a%20county-led%20survey%20in%202022%20that%20found%20that%2045%25%20of%20San%20Mateo's%20residents%20said%20they%20were%20suffering%20from%20loneliness%20and%20isolation%2C%20NBC%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESan%20Mateo%20County%2C%20with%20over%20700%2C000%20residents%2C%20in%20the%20San%20Francisco%20Bay%20Area%2C%20includes%20part%20of%20Silicon%20Valley.%20It%20has%20a%20large%20population%20of%20older%20residents%2C%20with%2018%25%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smcalltogetherbetter.org%2Fdemographicdata%3Fid%3D278%26sectionId%3D942%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecounty's%20population%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%2065%20%E2%80%94%202%25%20above%20the%20state%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20sort%20of%20a%20perfect%20storm%20for%20older%20adults%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Jennifer%20Steele%2C%20CEO%20of%20Meals%20on%20Wheels%20San%20Francisco%2C%20which%20delivers%20hot%20meals%20to%20older%20citizens%20in%20northern%20San%20Mateo%20County%2C%20told%20NBC%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20don't%20live%20close%20to%20their%20loved%20ones%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSometimes%20people%20have%20outlived%20their%20loved%20ones%20in%20some%20cases.%20Your%20social%20circle%20shrinks%20after%20retirement.%20It's%20harder%20for%20people%20to%20make%20friends.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Canepa%20is%20worried%20that%20the%20problem%20is%20not%20exclusive%20to%20older%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20teenagers%20and%20young%20adults%20in%20the%20county%20could%20also%20be%20at%20risk%2C%20partly%20due%20to%20the%20widespread%20use%20of%20social%20media%20and%20partly%20because%20of%20the%20high-pressure%20environment%20of%20Silicon%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECanepa%20said%20the%20resolution%20was%20just%20the%20first%20step%20towards%20finding%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20want%20to%20do%20is%20build%20on%20that.%20But%20we%20can't%20build%20on%20it%20if%20we%20don't%20make%20the%20investments%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabc7news.com%2Fsan-mateo-declares-loneliness-state-of-emergency-first-in-us-mental-health-depression%2F14373042%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EABC7%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-county-declares-loneliness-silicon-valley-public-health-emergency-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707061606000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65be672e7a3d271488776f7e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-county-declares-loneliness-silicon-valley-public-health-emergency-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22San%20Mateo%20county%20is%20one%20of%20the%20wealthiest%20in%20the%20US%2C%20hosting%20the%20headquarters%20of%20tech%20giants%20including%20Facebook%2C%20YouTube%2C%20and%20Electronic%20Arts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ashoaib%40insider.com%20(Alia%20Shoaib)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinside