C%20former%20England%20cricket%20team%20batter%20Kevin%20Pietersen%20was%20a%20bit%20critical%20of%20his%20technique.%20Pietersen%20was%20all%20praise%20for%20the%20youngster%20but%20also%20namedropped%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20and%20Ricky%20Ponting%20in%20his%20criticism%20of%20Gill's%20'lazy'%20technique.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20one%20technical%20flaw%20and%20that%20is%20that%20he%20is%20not%20busy%20enough%20before%20the%20ball%20is%20bowled.%20And%20it%20is%20an%20argument%20I%20have%20had%20with%20people%20around%2C%20whether%20you%20have%20the%20trigger%20or%20not%2C%20whether%20you%20get%20yourself%20into%20the%20game.%20I%20believe%20that%20in%20the%20Test%20match%20arena%2C%20bowlers%20are%20just%20that%20little%20bit%20quicker%20and%20they%20make%20you%20make%20decisions%20quicker.%20The%20step%20up%20is%20that%20he%20does%20need%20the%20trigger.%20Shubman%20Gill's%20batting%20is%20very...%20I%20would%20say%20almost%20lazy%20in%20the%20way%20that%20he%20stands%20at%20the%20crease%2C%26quot%3B%20Pietersen%20said%20on%20Jio%20Cinema.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20waits%20for%20the%20ball%20to%20be%20delivered%20before%20he%20makes%20any%20movement.%20And%20what%20I%20would%20like%20for%20him%20to%20see%20from%20him%20is%20that%20on%20the%20load%20up%2C%20just%20get%20a%20little%20bit%20ready.%20Look%20at%20all%20the%20great%20players.%20Tendulkar%20didn't%20do%20it%20that%20much%20but%20he%20did%20on%20occasions.%20Ricky%20Ponting%2C%20they%20say%2C%20didn't%20have%20a%20trigger%20but%20he%20did%20have%20a%20front-foot%20press.%20Even%20Lara.%20They%20all%20had%20a%20trigger%20and%20brought%20themselves%20into%20the%20game%20before%20the%20release.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShubman%20Gill%20scored%20a%20fine%20century%20to%20help%20India%20set%20a%20399-run%20target%20for%20England.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGill%20returned%20to%20form%2C%20scoring%20a%20timely%20104%20off%20147%20deliveries.%20All-rounders%20Axar%20Patel%20(45)%20and%20Ra