an%20two%20months%20because%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20the%20Deputy%C2%A0%20CM%20asked%20him%20not%20to%20speak%20about%20the%20resignation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhujbal%20reiterated%20that%20he%20was%20not%20opposed%20to%20Marathas%20getting%20the%20reservation%20but%20is%20against%20sharing%20the%20existing%20quota%20for%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20reporters%2C%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20chief%20minister%20will%20be%20able%20to%20clarify%2C%20but%20I%20can%20only%20say%20as%20of%20now%20that%20Bhujbal's%20resignation%20has%20not%20been%20accepted%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20or%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Sanjay%20Raut%20sought%20to%20know%20who%20has%20the%20authority%20to%20accept%20Bhujbal's%20resignation%20-%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20or%20Deputy%20CM%20Fadnavis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20a%20precedent%20that%20those%20who%20oppose%20the%20chief%20minister%20or%20the%20government%20have%20no%20right%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20it%2C%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20of%20the%20view%20that%20all%20communities%20should%20get%20their%20rights%20but%20not%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20encroaching%20on%20others'%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20Raut%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20even%20Mr%20Bhujbal%20says%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20at%20Antarwali%20Sarati%20village%20in%20Jalna%20district%2C%20Jarange%20rubbished%20Bhujbal's%20allegations%20that%20fake%20and%20overwritten%20records%20were%20being%20used%20to%20get%20the%20reservation%20for%20the%20Maratha%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20(Bhujbal)%20doesn't%20understand%20anything.%20There%20is%20a%20law%2C%20a%20government%2C%20a%20committee%20and%20scholars%20working%20on%20this%20issue%2C%20but%20Bhujbal%20doubts%20his%20own%20government.%20He%20is%20trying%20to%20damage%20Deputy%20Chief%20Ministers%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20and%20A