nt%2C%20Kamlesh%20claimed%20gold%20and%20silver%20jewellery%20worth%20lakhs%20and%20Rs%2025%2C000%20in%20cash%20were%20stolen%20from%20her%20home%20on%20January%2030%20between%202%20pm%20and%202%3A30%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20launched%20a%20problem%20but%20found%20no%20signs%20of%20forced%20entry%20-%20the%20locks%20on%20the%20main%20door%20and%20the%20cupboard%20were%20found%20to%20be%20intact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F681763c_stolen-jewellery-and-cash_625x300_04_February_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20then%20scoured%20through%20footage%20from%20CCTV%20cameras%20in%20the%20area%20and%20spotted%20a%20woman%20in%20a%20burqa%20entering%20the%20home%20suspiciously.%20The%20police's%20technical%20investigation%20led%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%2031-year-old%20Shweta%2C%20Kamlesh's%20elder%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%2C%20during%20questioning%2C%20revealed%20she%20planned%20this%20burglary%20because%20her%20mother%20loved%20her%20younger%20sister%20more%2C%20the%20police%20said.%20The%20feelings%20of%20jealousy%20and%20hatred%20overpowered%20her%2C%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20also%20had%20some%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShweta%20told%20the%20police%20she%20hatched%20this%20elaborate%20plan%20to%20pay%20off%20her%20dues.%20Some%20of%20the%20jewellery%20she%20stole%20was%20hers%2C%20which%20she%20had%20asked%20her%20mother%20to%20keep%2C%20while%20the%20rest%20were%20made%20by%20her%20mother%20for%20her%20sister's%20wedding%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20revealed%20how%20she%20slowly%20built%20up%20to%20the%20day%20of%20the%20robbery%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20Shwet