0%99%20The%20idea%20was%20to%20compare%20Mumbai%20with%20other%20international%20cities%20and%20chart%20out%20a%20plan%20for%20development%20for%20the%20next%20ten%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMcKinsey%20is%20known%20around%20the%20world%20as%20one%20of%20the%20great%20business%20success%20stories%20of%20recent%20times.%20Such%20is%20its%20prestige%2C%20that%20its%20staggering%20list%20of%20failures%20has%20been%20exorcised%20from%20public%20memory.%20The%20business%20journalist%20Duff%20McDonald%20wrote%20that%20McKinsey%E2%80%99s%20missteps%20would%20have%20%E2%80%98doomed%20lesser%20firms%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20since%20it%20hand-held%20companies%20like%20General%20Motors%2C%20Swissair%20and%20most%20notably%2C%20Enron%2C%20to%20their%20spectacular%20demise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%2020%20years%20of%20McKinsey%E2%80%99s%20recommendations%2C%20does%20Mumbai%20belong%20to%20McKinsey%E2%80%99s%20list%20of%20achievements%20or%20failures%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20all%2C%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20planners%20and%20managers%20have%20followed%20McKinsey%E2%80%99s%20advice%20closely.%20They%20have%20transformed%20Mumbai%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98consumption%20centre%E2%80%99%2C%20privatised%20the%20airport%2C%20eliminated%20octroi%2C%20expanded%20private%20transport%20infrastructure%20to%20connect%20business%20districts%2C%20selectively%20increased%20FSI%2C%20relaxed%20environmental%20and%20land%20regulations%2C%20and%20much%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20have%20even%20outdone%20McKinsey%20in%20some%20areas.%20For%20instance%2C%20McKinsey%20had%20advocated%20the%20recently%20launched%20Atal%20Setu%20MTHL%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98rail-cum-road%20link%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20the%20Metropolitan%20Development%20Authority%20(MMRDA)%20seems%20to%20have%20decided%20that%20because%20a%20railway%20will%20benefit%20low-income%20Mumbaikars%20more%20than%20consumers%20of%20cars%20and%20luxury%20real-estate%2C%20it%20should%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Enot%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20MTHL.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMcKinsey%E2%80%99s%20most%20visible%20contribution%20undoubtedly%20has%20been%20the%20three%20word%20justification%20for%20everything%20that%20benefits%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20political%2C%20bureaucratic%20and%20economic%20elite%3A%20%E2%80%98world%20class%20city.%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnderstandably%2C%20many%20critics%20have%20objected%20to%20this%20catchphrase%2C%20stating%20that%20such%20superficial%20comparisons%20with%20developed%20cities%20distract%20attention%20away%20from%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20real%20problems.%20Others%20have%20argued%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98world-class%20city%E2%80%99%20focus%20ignores%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20inequalities%2C%20and%20consequences%20of%20reforms%20on%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20poor.%20Some%20even%20believe%20that%20such%20comparisons%20are%20counterproductive%2C%20since%20every%20city%20is%20unique%2C%20and%20that%20no%20single%20model%20of%20urbanism%20is%20desirable%20or%20replicable%20around%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20criticisms%20may%20have%20a%20point.%20McKinsey%E2%80%99s%20recommendations%20cherry-picked%20examples%20from%20around%20the%20world%20to%20buttress%20a%20pro-privatisation%2C%20consumption%20led%20growth%20agenda%2C%20with%20no%20regard%20for%20the%20consequences%20on%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20workers%2C%20housing%20poor%20and%20the%20environment.%20But%20to%20assume%20that%20any%20comparison%20with%20other%20cities%20is%20illegitimate%20is%20itself%20a%20form%20of%20conservatism.%20There%20are%20lessons%20one%20can%20learn%20from%20other%20cities%2C%20provided%20we%20are%20conscious%20of%20their%20value%20and%20appropriateness%20to%20our%20own%20contexts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20purpose%20of%20a%20new%20book%2C%20titled%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E6%20Metros%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20authored%20by%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20highly%20acclaimed%20urban%20planner%20Shirish%20Patel%20%E2%80%93%20who%20incidentally%20was%20behind%20the%20%E2%80%98world-class%20city%E2%80%99%20of%20Navi%20Mumbai%20built%20in%20the%201970s%20%E2%80%93%20along%20with%20architects%20and%20urban%20designers%20Oormi%20Kapadia%20and%20Jasmine%20Saluja.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04170701%2FUntitled-design-9.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04170701%2FUntitled-design-9.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04170701%2FUntitled-design-9-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04170701%2FUntitled-design-9-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-695688%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%E2%80%986%20Metros%3A%20Urban%20Planning%20and%20Implementation%E2%80%99%20(in%20two%20volumes)%2C%20Shirish%20B%20Patel%2C%20Oormi%20Kapadia%2C%20and%20Jasmine%20Saluja%2C%20Vakils%2C%20Feffer%20%26amp%3B%20Simons%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3E6%20Metros%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20voluminous%20account%20of%20how%20six%20different%20cities%20of%20comparable%20size%20(London%2C%20New%20York%2C%20Tokyo%2C%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20Delhi%20and%20Mumbai)%20have%20evolved%20methods%20to%20address%20their%20urban%20development%20goals.%20These%20methods%20include%20institutional%20aspects%20of%20the%20planning%20process%2C%20implementation%2C%20land%20acquisition%20and%20regulation%3B%20issues%20of%20land%20allocation%20and%20development%20intensity%20in%20the%20form%20of%20land%20use%2C%20transit%2C%20housing%2C%20social%20infrastructure%20(open%20spaces%2C%20health%2C%20education%2C%20social%20amenities)%20and%20density%3B%20and%20experiential%20dimensions%20of%20the%20city%20that%20are%20shaped%20by%20guidelines%20that%20shape%20urban%20form%20and%20fabric.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20book%20may%20seem%20to%20some%20as%20an%20academic%20exercise%20of%20comparing%20six%20cities%20based%20on%20various%20urban%20planning%20parameters.%20But%20this%20would%20be%20a%20mistake.%20In%20fundamental%20ways%2C%20this%20is%20a%20book%20about%20Mumbai.%20The%20three%20authors%20of%20this%20book%20live%20and%20practice%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20the%20various%20issues%20identified%20in%20the%20book%20reflect%20the%20authors%E2%80%99%20concerns%20as%20professionals%20and%20activists%20with%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20problems.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20book%20is%20an%20evaluation%20of%20Mumbai%20with%20reference%20to%20other%20cities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20is%20the%20planning%20process%20organised%20in%20other%20cities%3F%20Those%20familiar%20with%20Mumbai%20recognise%20that%20while%20the%20Brihanmumbai%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(BMC)%20is%20responsible%20for%20overall%20urban%20management%20of%20the%20city%2C%20the%20periodic%20incursions%20of%20the%20state%20government%20in%20planning%20regulations%20and%20through%20its%20various%20parastatal%20%E2%80%98authorities%E2%80%99%20have%20affected%20a%20territorial%20and%20functional%20fragmentation%20of%20the%20planning%20process.%20These%20%E2%80%98authorities%E2%80%99%20independently%20pursue%20their%20projects%20and%20plans%2C%20often%20ignoring%20or%20even%20conflicting%20with%20each%20other.%20Sometimes%2C%20the%20result%20is%20a%20downward%20spiral%20of%20absurdity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20original%20proposal%20for%20the%20northern%20section%20of%20the%20Coastal%20Road%20project%20was%20debated%20as%20a%20choice%20between%20two%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ealternatives%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20a%20sea-link%20and%20a%20road%20along%20the%20coast%20with%20a%20combination%20of%20reclaimed%20and%20stilted%20sections.%20Eventually%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eboth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20these%20alternatives%20will%20be%20constructed%2C%20by%20three%20separate%20agencies%3A%20a%20Coastal%20Road%20from%20Versova%20to%20Dahisar%20constructed%20by%20the%20MCGM%2C%20a%20sea-link%20from%20Bandra%20to%20Versova%20by%20the%20MSRDC%2C%20and%20an%20extension%20of%20that%20sea-link%20from%20Versova%20to%20Vasai-Virar%20to%20be%20built%20by%20MMRDA.%20It%20is%20significant%20that%20the%20sea-link%20from%20Bandra%20to%20Virar%20does%20not%20appear%20in%20the%20MMRDA%E2%80%99s%202016%20Regional%20Plan%2C%20nor%20in%20the%20BMC%E2%80%99s%202018%20Development%20Plan.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20MSRDC%20and%20MMRDA%20will%20be%20executing%20their%20projects%20contrary%20to%20statutory%20plans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThrough%20their%20study%20of%20six%20cities%2C%20the%20authors%20of%20%3Cem%3E6%20Metros%3C%2Fem%3E%20advocate%20a%20solution%20to%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98balkanised%E2%80%99%20planning%20system%20by%20shifting%20decision-making%20and%20accountability%20to%20elected%20representatives%20at%20the%20local%20levels%3A%20a%20Mayoral%20level%20that%20deals%20with%20issues%20of%20the%20city%20such%20as%20transit%2C%20infrastructure%20and%20services%2C%20and%20a%20Municipal%20Councillor%20level%20that%20deals%20with%20detailed%20local-area%20planning%20supported%20by%20technical%20inputs%20where%20necessary.%20Although%20outside%20the%20scope%20of%20their%20book%2C%20we%20could%20by%20extension%20envision%20the%20allocation%20of%20functions%20to%20a%20Metropolitan%20level%20planning%20board%2C%20composed%20of%20elected%20city%20representatives%2C%20to%20oversee%20various%20aspects%20of%20metropolitan%20management.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04170934%2FScreenshot-2024-02-04-at-5.09.18%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04170934%2FScreenshot-2024-02-04-at-5.09.18%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04170934%2FScreenshot-2024-02-04-at-5.09.18%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x215.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04170934%2FScreenshot-2024-02-04-at-5.09.18%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x732.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-695689%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22858%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20core%20concern%20of%20the%20book%2C%20and%20the%20main%20axis%20of%20comparative%20analysis%20between%20different%20cities%2C%20is%20the%20question%20of%20land.%20How%20do%20other%20cities%20administer%20urban%20land%3F%20This%20is%20a%20question%20that%20is%20most%20lucidly%20discussed%20in%20the%20first%20chapter%20of%20the%20book%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98core%20beliefs.%E2%80%99%20The%20land%20market%2C%20they%20argue%2C%20calls%20for%20entirely%20different%20forms%20of%20regulation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20authors%20recommend%20a%20policy%20of%20land%20pricing%20that%20ranges%20from%20fully%20marketised%20land%20to%20price%20controls%20that%20make%20land%20affordable%20for%20lower%20income%20groups%2C%20to%20land%20that%20is%20taken%20off%20the%20market%2C%20reserved%20specifically%20for%20economically%20weaker%20sections%20of%20society.%20They%20observe%20that%20such%20practices%20are%20explicit%20in%20public%20and%20social%20housing%20schemes%2C%20and%20are%20implicit%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98inclusionary%20housing%E2%80%99%20policies%20of%20other%20cities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20inclusionary%20housing%2C%20a%20developer%20or%20land%20owner%20supplies%20a%20portion%20of%20their%20land%20for%20affordable%20housing%20as%20the%20condition%20for%20the%20commercial%20exploitation%20of%20the%20rest.%20In%20Catalonia%2C%20Spain%2C%20they%20note%2C%2050%25%20of%20floor%20space%20offered%20for%20sale%20is%20set%20aside%20for%20affordable%20housing%2C%20and%20in%20London%20it%20is%2035%25.%20It%20must%20be%20noted%20that%20for%20inclusionary%20housing%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20construction%20is%20fully%20reimbursed%20to%20the%20developer%2C%20allowing%20the%20public%20authority%20to%20enforce%20adherence%20to%20adequate%20standards.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20different%20from%20%E2%80%98redevelopment%E2%80%99%20schemes%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20where%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20replacement%20%E2%80%98free%20house%E2%80%99%20(which%20can%20be%20put%20back%20on%20the%20market)%2C%20and%20therefore%20the%20cost%20of%20land%20and%20construction%20is%20passed%20on%20to%20new%20flat%20buyers.%20This%20has%20resulted%20in%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20reconstruction%2C%20poor%20quality%20rehabilitation%2C%20and%20a%20rather%20small%20increment%20in%20new%20house%20supply%20which%20in%20turn%20is%20affordable%20only%20for%20the%20astronomically%20wealthy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20must%20be%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20authors%20of%20%3Cem%3E6%20Metros%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20not%20simply%20peddling%20new%20%E2%80%98ideas%E2%80%99%20to%20solve%20complex%20urban%20problems.%20By%20making%20land%20governance%20and%20regulation%20the%20focus%20of%20their%20arguments%2C%20they%20hope%20for%20a%20shift%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Epriorities%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20urban%20planning%2C%20from%20one%20oriented%20towards%20profit%20at%20all%20costs%2C%20to%20one%20that%20sets%20up%20a%20sensible%20framework%20of%20regulations%20to%20achieve%20equitable%20and%20sustainable%20development.%20As%20they%20write%20in%20their%20introduction%2C%20%E2%80%98when%20it%20comes%20to%20land%2C%20there%20are%20other%20considerations%20that%20far%20outweigh%20the%20promised%20efficiency%20of%20markets.%E2%80%99%20It%20is%20the%20delineation%20of%20these%20%E2%80%98other%20considerations%E2%80%99%20and%20their%20achievement%2C%20that%20forms%20the%20main%20preoccupation%20of%20the%20book.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20acknowledge%2C%20however%2C%20that%20good%20regulation%20hinges%20on%20governments%20and%20government%20agencies%20that%20act%20impartially%2C%20competently%2C%20and%20in%20the%20pursuit%20of%20the%20public%20interest.%20Government%20agencies%20are%20not%20equivalent%20to%20private%20developers%20who%20aim%20to%20maximise%20profits%20from%20land.%20Unless%20this%20condition%20is%20ensured%2C%20they%20write%2C%20%E2%80%98all%20we%20can%20do%20is%20extend%20our%20condolences%20to%20that%20city%20and%20hope%20for%20a%20change%20in%20its%20political%20and%20bureaucratic%20leadership.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwenty%20years%20ago%2C%20McKinsey%E2%80%99s%20influential%20%E2%80%98world%20class%20city%E2%80%99%20document%20for%20Mumbai%20demanded%20an%20urgent%20implementation%20of%20its%20recommendations%20otherwise%20it%20was%20in%20%E2%80%98grave%20danger%20of%20collapsing%20completely.%E2%80%99%20It%20picked%20examples%20from%20other%20cities%20to%20make%20a%20case%20to%20%E2%80%98actively%20focus%20on%20economic%20growth%2C%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98high-impact%20projects%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98public%20private%20partnerships%2C%E2%80%99%20and%20a%20empowered%20administration%20to%20drive%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20transformation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3E6%20Metros%3C%2Fem%3E%20shows%2C%20in%20contrast%2C%20what%20intelligent%20observers%20can%20learn%20from%20other%20cities%2C%20and%20what%20we%20can%20do%20to%20improve%20our%20own.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fhussain%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHussain%20Indorewala%3C%2Fa%3E%20teaches%20at%20the%20Kamla%20Raheja%20Vidyanidhi%20Institute%20of%20Architecture%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707048001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04171152%2F25962558110_f6f55734b5_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Flessons-for-mumbai-land-six-metros%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%2C%20well%20researched%20book%20by%20three%20architects%20and%20activists%20shows%20what%20Mumbai%20can%20and%20should%20learn%20from%20other%20cities%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Flessons-for-mumbai-land-six-metros%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meet%20the%20latest%20addition%20to%20the%20Deol%20family%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707047835000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107403412%2Cimgsize-59786.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdharmendras-granddaughter-ties-the-knot-rushabh-shah-wedding%2Farticleshow%2F107403455.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107403455.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ENikita%20Chaudhary%20is%20the%20daughter%20of%20Ajeeta%20Deol%2C%20Dharmendra%20and%20Prakash%20Kaur's%20eldest%20daughter.%20Ajeeta%2C%20who%20married%20Dr.%20Kiran%20Chaudhary%2C%20a%20dentist%20based%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20resides%20in%20California.%20Nikita%20has%20an%20older%20sister%20named%20Priyanka%2C%20and%20both%20siblings%20pursue%20careers%20in%20dentistry%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdharmendras-granddaughter-ties-the-knot-rushabh-shah-wedding%2Farticleshow%2F107403455.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Woman%20Accused%20Of%20Having%20Sex%20With%20Two%20Teenagers%20After%20Spat%20With%20Husband%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2038-year-old%20woman%20in%20the%20US%20was%20charged%20Friday%20with%20criminal%20sexual%20conduct%20after%20allegedly%20having%20sexual%20contact%20with%20two%2015-year-old%20boys.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F02%2F04%2Fnews%2Fmarried-minnesota-mom-accused-of-having-sex-with-two-15-year-old-boys-at-hotel-after-fight-with-husband%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Allison%20Leigh%20Schardin%2C%20a%C2%A0mother%20of%20two%2C%20was%20staying%20at%20the%20same%20hotel%20in%20Roseville%20as%20a%20boys'%20hockey%20team%20from%20Colorado.%20As%20per%20court%20documents%2C%C2%A0she%20started%20chatting%20to%20the%20teens%20in%20the%20hotel%20hot%20tub%20on%20January%2014%2C%20telling%20them%20about%20her%20marital%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%20of%20them%20went%20back%20to%20their%20rooms%2C%20she%20sent%20one%20of%20the%20boys%20a%20Snapchat%20text%20saying%20that%20she%20had%20just%20had%20a%20fight%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20wanted%20to%20come%20to%20the%20teen's%20room.%20She%20reportedly%20asked%20the%20boys%20their%20ages%20and%20commented%20they%20were%20young%20enough%20to%20be%20her%20children