-1235896737%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Frotterdam-toshihiko-tanaka-rei-shumari-1235896737%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Existing%20taxation%20structure%20for%20corporates%20very%20reasonable%3A%20Revenue%20secy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707042860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2021-01%2F14%2Ffull%2F1610565102-1988.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fexisting-taxation-structure-for-corporates-very-reasonable-revenue-secy-124020400329_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Companies%20opting%20for%20these%20new%20tax%20rates%20had%20to%20forego%20all%20exemptions%20and%20incentives.%20The%20effective%20tax%20rate%20for%20existing%20units%2C%20after%20considering%20surcharges%20and%20cess%20--%20such%20as%20Swachh%20Bharat%20cess%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fexisting-taxation-structure-for-corporates-very-reasonable-revenue-secy-124020400329_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fexisting-taxation-structure-for-corporates-very-reasonable-revenue-secy-124020400329_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fexisting-taxation-structure-for-corporates-very-reasonable-revenue-secy-124020400329_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Past%2C%20Present%20and%20Future%20of%20Resistance%20in%20Myanmar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F10235624%2FProtest_in_Myanmar_against_Military_Coup_14-Feb-2021_05.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20civil%20war%20in%20Myanmar%20entered%20its%20fourth%20year%20on%20February%201%20and%20has%20been%20fanning%20unrest%20and%20insurgency%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20northeast.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnion%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20decision%20last%20month%20to%20fence%20the%20entire%201%2C643-km%20border%20with%20Myanmar%20and%20suspend%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ffencing-border-with-myanmar-ending-free-movement-regime-soon-amit-shah%5C%22%3EFree%20Movement%20Regime%3C%2Fa%3E%20(FMR)%20has%20been%20rejected%20by%20both%20chief%20ministers%20of%20Nagaland%20and%20Mizoram%20as%20these%20measures%20will%20divide%20their%20kith%20and%20kin%20across%20the%20border.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20last%20few%20months%2C%20fighting%20between%20the%20junta%20and%20resistance%20forces%20spilled%20over%20to%20north%20east%20from%20Rakhine%20and%20Arakan%20states%20in%20Myanmar%20and%20nearly%20800%20junta%20soldiers%20who%20had%20taken%20refuge%20on%20the%20Indian%20side%20were%20flown%20back.%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20insurgent%20groups%20sheltering%20in%20border%20regions%20of%20Myanmar%20have%20exploited%20the%20intense%20violence%20(since%20early%20May%20last%20year)%20that%20has%20been%20fuelled%20by%20the%20loss%20of%206%2C000%20weapons%20from%20Manipur%20state%20armouries.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20has%20been%20grossly%20mismanaged%20by%20state%20and%20central%20authorities%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20once%20dormant%20eastern%20border%20has%20become%20live%20and%20vulnerable%20due%20to%20the%20junta%20losing%20operational%20control%20to%20resistance%20forces.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20coup%20in%20February%202021%20is%20the%20sixth%20successful%20coup%20since%201962%20by%20Myanmarese%20military%2C%20also%20called%20Tatmadaw%20or%20Sit%20Tat.%20Junta%20forces%20have%20inflicted%20coups%20more%20times%20than%20any%20other%20military%20in%20the%20world%20with%20profound%20expertise.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20a%20national%20resistance%20has%20been%20cobbled%20to%20try%20to%20unhinge%20the%20military%20rule%20though%20the%20opposition%20has%20not%20thought%20about%20the%20end%20game.%20Resistance%20forces%20consist%20of%20Ethnic%20Armed%20Organisations%20(EAOs)%2C%20local%20militias%2C%20and%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Defence%20Force%20(PDF)%2C%20a%20majority%20Burman%20ethnic%20group%20created%20by%20the%20National%20League%20of%20Democracy%E2%80%99s%20parallel%20National%20Unity%20Government%20(NUG).%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEAOs%20have%20enjoyed%20autonomy%20following%20ceasefire%20agreements%20with%20the%20military.%20Not%20all%20have%20submitted%20to%20ceasefire%20arrangements%2C%20though.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20powerful%20Arakan%20Army%20(AA)%20which%20operates%20in%20Rakhine%2C%20Chin%20and%20Arakan%20states%20broke%20its%20ceasefire%20in%20November%20last%20year%20and%20went%20on%20the%20offensive%20to%20defeat%20the%20junta%20in%20these%20two%20states.%20It%20is%20believed%20that%20Rohingyas%20may%20have%20joined%20AA.%20The%20Chin%20National%20Army%20also%20operates%20in%20this%20region.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fmyanmar-junta-arakan-army-resistance%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20Armed%20Resistance%20Is%20Testing%20Myanmar%20Junta%E2%80%99s%20Grip%20on%20Power%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETake%20a%20look%20back.%20On%20September%207%2C%202022%2C%20the%20Special%20Advisory%20Council%20of%20International%20Experts%20Supporting%20Democracy%20released%20a%20paper%20which%20showed%20that%20the%20junta%20control%2072%20of%20333%20major%20towns%20and%2017%25%20of%20land%20area.%20The%20EAOs%20were%20reportedly%20controlling%2052%25%20of%20territory%20while%2023%25%20was%20contested.%20Those%20were%20early%20days.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20major%20offensives%20were%20launched%20in%20October%20and%20November%20last%20year%20called%201027%20and%201111%2C%20(the%20last%20two%20figures%20denoting%20month%20and%20next%20two%20figures%20the%20date%20of%20operation)%20by%20an%20alliance%20of%20three%20EAOs%20along%20with%20PDF%20and%20militias.%20These%20operations%20stretched%20from%20Rakhine%20in%20the%20south%C2%A0%20to%20all%20of%20the%20northeast%20up%20till%20Lashio.%20The%20AA%20seized%20control%20of%20territory%20bordering%20India%20including%20Sagaing%20region%2C%20pockets%20in%20Mandalay%20and%20Bago.%20The%20biggest%20setback%20for%20the%20junta%20was%20in%20the%20northern%20Shan%20state%20and%20Kokang%20Special%20Region%20where%20it%20lost%20Laukkai%2C%20one%20of%20its%20seven%20operational%20command%20centres.%20The%20Myanmar%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20Army%20(MNDAA)%20which%20spearheaded%20attacks%20in%20the%20north%2C%20scored%20major%20successes%20and%20closed%20down%20five%20border%20trade%20centres%20and%20crossing%20points%20with%20China.%20A%20number%20of%20Chinese%20living%20in%20the%20north%20had%20to%20flee%20to%20Yunnan%20(China).%20General%20Peng%20Deren%2C%20commander%20of%20the%20MNDAA%2C%20said%20wresting%20control%20of%20the%20north%20from%20the%20junta%20and%20restoring%20its%20writ%20to%20end%20criminal%20activities%20was%20sweet%20revenge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Chinese%2C%20after%20a%20series%20of%20negotiations%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fmyanmar-china-ceasefire-guerrillas-b60aa673a2fc38cd04e7dd781e3625c5%5C%22%3Ebrokered%20a%20ceasefire%20with%20the%20junta%20on%20January%2012%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20some%20EAOs%20in%20MNDAA%20did%20not%20acknowledge.%20Clearly%20these%20offensives%20in%20the%20north%20and%20northeast%20could%20not%20have%20been%20launched%20without%20Chinese%20complicity.%20For%20some%20time%20now%2C%20the%20Chinese%20have%20wanted%20to%20stop%20and%20eliminate%20various%20drug%20and%20gambling%20rackets%20that%20have%20been%20going%20on%20with%20the%20knowledge%20and%20possible%20cooperation%20of%20the%20military.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJunta%20retaliation%20to%20its%20losses%20has%20come%20mainly%20through%20artillery%20shelling%2C%20strafing%20by%20helicopters%20and%20jets%20of%20towns%20that%20it%20evacuated%20after%20being%20outgunned.%20Many%20Brigadier%20Generals%2C%20Colonels%20and%20soldiers%20surrendered%20without%20fighting.%20Sui%20Lee%20Wei%20writing%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20December%2023%2C%20reported%20that%20around%204%2C500%20(this%20figure%20often%20varies%20and%20rises%20to%206%2C000%20in%20some%20accounts)%20personnel%20could%20have%20defected%20among%20a%20total%20of%2021%2C000%20estimated%20casualties.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20junta%20does%20not%20reveal%20its%20losses%20but%20experts%20estimate%20that%20Junta%20strength%20is%20still%20around%20300%2C000%20to%20400%2C000%20soldiers%20with%20modern%20weapons.%20They%20are%20encountering%20difficulties%20in%20making%20up%20shortfalls%20as%20last%20year%2C%20only%2083%20cadets%20joined%20the%20defence%20academy%20compared%20to%201%2C000%20in%202022.%20On%20New%20Year%E2%80%99s%20day%2C%20coup%20General%20Min%20Aung%20Hlaing%20issued%20honorary%20titles%20for%20combatants%20and%20praised%20the%20junta%20forces%20for%20their%20dedication.%20Hlaing%20offered%20a%20political%20resolution%20to%20resistance%20forces%20asking%20them%20to%20stop%20fighting%20a%20war%20they%20could%20not%20win.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fembed%3Fpb%3D!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d29952.794809809635!2d93.1128213214015!3d20.213192149322396!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x30b0fed487d693c5%253A0xb745b464807ad06d!2sPauktaw%252C%2520Myanmar%2520(Burma)!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1707042115693!5m2!1sen!2sin%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20last%20big%20win%20for%20EAOs%20was%20by%20AA%20in%20Pauktaw%20close%20to%20Sittwe%2C%20where%20India%20operates%20its%20deep%20sea%20port%20for%20implementing%20its%20Act%20East%20policy%20that%20includes%20constructing%20infrastructure%20like%20the%20multi-modal%20Kaladan%20river%20project.%20Paletwa%20town%20which%20rests%20on%20Kaladan%20was%20captured%20by%20AA%20earlier%20this%20month%20and%20is%20key%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20trilateral%20highway%20from%20Moreh%20in%20India%20to%20Moe%20Sat%20(Thailand)%20passing%20through%20Sagaing%20region.%20So%20now%2C%20AA%20has%20become%20the%20key%20interlocutor%20for%20New%20Delhi%20to%20ensure%20peace%20and%20stability%20in%20its%20border%20in%20Rakhine%20and%20Arakan%20states%20and%20Sagaing%20region%2C%20the%20areas%20it%20controls.%20New%20Delhi%20should%20recalibrate%20its%20policy%20towards%20the%20junta.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20naval%20base%20at%20Sittwe%20under%20threat%2C%20(members%20of%20the%20Pauktaw%20garrison%20are%20known%20to%20have%20escaped%20by%20boat%20on%20January%2019)%20the%20junta%20has%20lost%20control%20of%20an%20arc%20of%20territory%20covering%20Myanmar%20borders%20with%20India%20and%20China%20including%20loss%20of%20trade%20with%20China.%20Fighting%20had%20crept%20towards%20Junta%20headquarters%20at%20its%20new%20capital%20Naypitaw%20but%20is%20still%20some%20200%20km%20to%20its%20north.%20Most%20of%20the%20central%20and%20southern%20regions%20as%20also%20bordering%20Thailand%20is%20under%20Naypitaw%20control.%20The%20Bamar%20heartland%20is%20the%20Yangon%20valley.%20The%20junta%E2%80%99s%20naval%20and%20air%20bases%20are%20in%20this%20region.%20The%20losses%20by%20any%20count%20are%20significant%20and%20can%20be%20described%20as%20a%20strategic%20shift%20in%20direction%20of%20civil%20war%20and%20in%20relative%20balance%20of%20power%20resulting%20from%20tactical%20defeats.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20resistance%E2%80%99s%20successes%20are%20outstanding%2C%20they%20do%20not%20represent%20military%20victory.%20The%20resistance%20would%20have%20to%20capture%20a%20major%20air%20base%20and%20secure%20key%20pockets%20in%20Yangon%20to%20pose%20an%20existential%20threat%20to%20junta.%20Further%2C%20despite%20desertions%20and%20defections%2C%20cohesion%20of%20military%20formations%20who%20realise%20they%20have%20high%20stakes%20in%20the%20war%20are%20intact%3A%20so%20are%20the%20elite%20divisions%20not%20committed%20in%20battle.%20But%20the%20next%20round%20of%20fighting%20will%20be%20in%20and%20around%20Sittwe%20and%20that%20may%20be%20the%20clincher.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fthree-years-of-coup-in-myanmar-what-explains-indias-pro-junta-position%5C%22%3EThree%20Years%20of%20Coup%20in%20Myanmar%3A%20What%20Explains%20India%E2%80%99s%20Pro-Junta%20Position%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEAOs%20in%20the%20resistance%20have%20dominant%20interests%20mainly%20confined%20to%20their%20states%20or%20regions%20and%20seek%20bigger%20influence%20with%20Naypitaw%20to%20enhance%20their%20autonomy.%20General%20Deren%E2%80%99s%20New%20Year%20statement%20indicated%20that%20MNDAA%20has%20achieved%20its%20objective.%20A%20resistance%20alliance%20that%20will%20venture%20into%20the%20heartland%20is%20unlikely%20to%20take%20shape.%20Further%2C%20EAOs%20have%C2%A0%20political%20differences%20though%20they%20can%20cooperate%20militarily%2C%20but%20locally.%20Although%20the%20current%20initiative%20and%20momentum%20are%20with%20the%20resistance%2C%20their%20differences%20with%20NUG%20is%20another%20impediment%20to%20military%20unity.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChina%2C%20which%20has%20big%20political%20and%20economic%20interests%20in%20Myanmar%20will%20not%20allow%20defenestration%20of%20junta%20forces.%20Along%20with%20Russia%20it%20will%20double%20down%20on%20providing%20military%20and%20economic%20support%20to%20Junta.%20Beijing%20has%20strong%20links%20and%20influence%20with%20EAOs%20like%20AA%20whom%20it%20has%20been%20supplying%20weapons.%20China%20will%20be%20a%20key%20actor%20in%20any%20long%20term%20political%20solution%2C%20not%20just%20because%20it%20is%20the%20dominant%20external%20player%20but%20also%20due%20to%20its%20huge%20political%20and%20economic%20investments.%20While%20it%20has%20a%20love-hate%20relationship%20with%20the%20military%20it%20also%20enjoyed%20friendly%20and%20stable%20relations%20with%20the%20democratic%20polity%20post%202011%20during%20the%20hybrid%20rule%20era.%20China%20will%20want%20a%20cohesive%20Army%20to%20keep%20the%20country%20together%20as%20it%20has%20since%201948.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20its%20back%20to%20the%20wall%2C%20the%20junta%20has%20no%20good%20options%20to%20break%20the%20stalemate.%20Two%20main%20choices%20are%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3Ea)%20A%20negotiated%20political%20solution%20under%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fhow-aseans-failed-five-point-consensus-has-let-down-the-people-of-myanmar%5C%22%3EASEAN%E2%80%99s%20Five-Point%20Consensus%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20time%20is%20not%20on%20its%20side%20the%20junta%20will%20try%20to%20secure%20an%20end%20to%20fighting%20%E2%80%93%20a%20ceasefire%20followed%20by%20cessation%20of%20hostilities.%20Although%20the%20balance%20of%20advantage%20is%20with%20the%20resistance%2C%20Junta%20forces%20are%20as%20yet%20invincible.%20But%20a%20political%20solution%20acceptable%20to%20the%20NUG%20and%20democratic%20forces%20must%20result%20in%20a%20significantly%20diminished%20role%20for%20military%20in%20governance%20and%20politics.%20For%20example%20it%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20represented%20by%20a%20political%20party%20with%2025%25%20seat%20reservation%3B%20ministers%20of%20defence%2C%20interior%20and%20border%20%E2%80%93%20hitherto%20from%20military%20%E2%80%93%20must%20be%20civilians%3B%20and%20the%202008%20military-drafted%20constitution%20suspended.%20This%20climbdown%20by%20military%20will%20not%20be%20easy%20to%20negotiate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3Eb)%20The%20second%20option%20is%20to%20keep%20fighting%20and%20broker%20ceasefire%20deals%20with%20EAOs%20in%20order%20to%20break%20the%20unity%20among%20the%20resistance.%20The%20junta%20cannot%20afford%20to%20lose%20the%20war%20as%20that%20holds%20the%20spectre%20of%20generals%20facing%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20at%20the%20Hague%20over%20allegations%20of%20genocide%20against%20the%20Rohingya%20in%202019%20and%20Burmans%20during%20the%20civil%20war.%20The%20United%20Nations%20has%20in%20its%20contingency%20planning%20cupboard%20for%20fragile%20and%20failing%20states%2C%20detailed%20plans%20for%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20day%20after%E2%80%9D.%20I%20have%20seen%20one%20for%20Afghanistan%20in%202015%20when%20the%20end%20game%20was%20being%20explored.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAshok%20K.%20Mehta%2C%20a%20major%20general%2C%20is%20a%20founding%20member%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20Defence%20Planning%20Staff%2C%20now%20the%20Integrated%20Defence%20Staff.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707042592000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F10235624%2FProtest_in_Myanmar_against_Military_Coup_14-Feb-2021_05.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fthe-past-present-and-future-of-resistance-in-myanmar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Will%20the%20junta%20keep%20fighting%20and%20broker%20ceasefire%20deals%20with%20resistance%20groups%3F%20Or%20will%20it%20try%20a%20diplomatic%20solution%20to%20broker%20an%20end%20to%20fighting%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fthe-past-present-and-future-of-resistan