C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MLA's%20Big%20Remarks%20On%20Hemant%20Soren%20Ahead%20Of%20Jharkhand%20Majority%20Test%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere's%20many%20a%20slip%20'twixt%20the%20cup%20and%20the%20lip.%20This%20proverb%20holds%20true%20for%20the%20current%20situation%20in%20Jharkhand.%20Champai%20Soren%20has%20claimed%20the%20support%20of%2047%20MLAs%20of%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%2C%20Congress%20and%20RJD%20and%20taken%20oath%20as%20Chief%20Minister.%20Tomorrow%2C%20he%20faces%20a%20majority%20test%20in%20the%20Assembly%2C%20and%20latest%20developments%20indicate%20the%20battle%20is%20far%20from%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2047%20MLAs%2C%20one%20has%20come%20out%20strongly%20against%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20whose%20resignation%20set%20off%20the%20process%20for%20a%20new%20government%20formation.%20Another%20JMM%20legislator%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20is%20off%20the%20grid%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20skip%20the%20floor%20test%20tomorrow.%20The%20JMM%2C%20busy%20keeping%20its%20flock%20of%20MLAs%20together%2C%20has%20stressed%20that%20it%20has%20adequate%20numbers%20to%20cross%20the%20majority%20mark%20in%20the%2081-member%20Assembly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20JMM%20MLA%20today%20said%20Hemant%20Soren%20had%20ignored%20his%20advice%20and%20that%20landed%20him%20in%20jail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELobin%20Hembrom%2C%20who%20represents%20Borio%20seat%20in%20Sahibganj%20district%2C%20was%20at%20an%20event%20organised%20by%20a%20non-political%20organisation.%20Speaking%20to%20the%20media%20on%20the%20sidelines%2C%20Mr%20Hembrom%20said%20the%20JMM%20manifesto%20ahead%20of%20the%202019%20state%20polls%20had%20promised%20the%20implementation%20of%20Chota%20Nagpur%20Tenancy%20Act%20and%20Santhal%20Parganas%20Tenancy%20Act.%20The%20JMM%20MLA%20also%20said%20the%20central%20law%2C%20Panchayat%20(Extension%20to%20Scheduled%20Areas)%C2%A0Act%2C%201996%2C%20has%20not%20been%20implemented%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20first%20two%20laws%20are%20aimed%20at%20protecting%20land%20rights%20of%20tribals%2C%20the%20PESA%20Act%20empowers%20the%20gram%20sabha%20to%20protect%20tribals%20from%20exploitation.%20%26quot%3BThe%20gram%20sabha%20has%20no%20power%20now.%20If%20the%20PESA%20Act%20was%20implemented%2C%20it%20would%20be%20more%20powerful.%20When%20none%20of%20these%20shields%20(for%20tribals)%20was%20implemented%2C%20we%20were%20forced%20to%20form%20this%20forum%2C%20Jharkhand%20Bachao%20Morcha%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legislator%20said%20he%20would%20sever%20all%20ties%20from%20JMM.%20%26quot%3BJharkhand%20was%20formed%20after%20such%20a%20struggle%20under%20Shibu%20Soren.%20But%20even%20today%2C%20these%20issues%20have%20not%20been%20resolved%20at%20the%20ground.%20People%20are%20now%20calling%20me%20a%20traitor%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHemant%20Soren%2C%20who%20is%20being%20investigated%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20land%20scam%20case%2C%20resigned%20late%20on%20Wednesday.%20Champai%20Soren%20took%20over%20after%20claiming%20support%20of%2047%20MLAs%20from%20JMM%2C%20Congress%20and%20RJD.%20He%20needs%20to%20prove%20his%20government's%20majority%20in%20the%20House%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Hembrom%20said%20he%20would%20now%20see%20how%20the%20state%20government%20under%20Champai%20Soren%20functions.%20He%20added%20that%20he%20would%20keep%20raising%20these%20issues%20in%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20land%20scam%20allegations%2C%20in%20which%20connection%20Mr%20Soren%20has%20been%20arrested%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20have%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20irregularities.%20IAS%20officers%20are%20involved.%20Nobody%20can%20touch%20that%20land.%20This%20means%20that%20CNT%20Act%20is%20not%20in%20force.%20Now%20people%20are%20going%20to%20jail.%20Eventually%2C%20our%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20also%20sent%20to%20jail.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MLA%20said%20he%20had%20spoken%20to%20Hemant%20Soren%20on%20this%20issue.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20warned%20him%20that%20the%20people%20around%20him%20are%20maligning%20his%20image%20and%20he%20should%20be%20careful.%20He%20replied%20that%20I%20speak%20nonsense%20and%20this%20gives%20an%20opportunity%20to%20the%20Opposition.%20I%20had%20then%20told%20him%20that%20he%20and%20Shibu%20Soren%20are%20my%20leaders%20and%20I%20cannot%20tolerate%20your%20disrespect.%20If%20he%20had%20heeded%20my%20advice%2C%20he%20would%20not%20have%20seen%20this%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Hembrom%20said%20the%20state%20government%20has%20snatched%20the%20land%20of%20tribals%20in%20the%20name%20of%20airport%2C%20dams%20and%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Borio%20MLA%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Jharkhand%20government%20is%20led%20by%20a%20tribal%2C%20but%20run%20by%20non-tribals.%20%26quot%3BWe%20wanted%20a%20tribal%20Chief%20Minister.%20We%20got%20one.%20But%20everything%20is%20done%20by%20Biharis.%20I%20have%20raised%20this%20multiple%20times%2C%20but%20Hemant%20Soren%20did%20not%20respond%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJMM%20general%20secretary%20Supriyo%20Bhattacharya%20said%20they%20have%20spoken%20to%20Mr%20Hembrom.%20%26quot%3BHe%20will%20be%20coming%20for%20the%20floor%20test%20tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20MLA%2C%20Chamra%20Linda%20from%20Bishunpur%20constituency%2C%20cannot%20be%20contacted%2C%20it%20is%20learnt.%20Mr%20Linda%20was%20also%20absent%20at%20party%20meetings%20held%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20majority%20test.%20While%20JMM%20leaders%20said%20he%20was%20unwell%2C%20sources%20revealed%20that%20the%20party%20leaders%20have%20failed%20to%20contact%20the%20legislator.%20Earlier%2C%20Mr%20Linda%20too%20had%20attacked%20the%20JMM%20government%20and%20said%20it%20had%20not%20taken%20any%20firm%20step%20for%20tribal%20welfare%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707040140000%2C%22v