%2Fparamount-cables-q3-results-net-profit-climbs-54-to-rs-22-crore-124020400260_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It's%20expenses%20stood%20at%20Rs%20263.77%20crore%20as%20against%20Rs%20207.68%20crore%20year%20on%20year%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fparamount-cables-q3-results-net-profit-climbs-54-to-rs-22-crore-124020400260_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fparamount-cables-q3-results-net-profit-climbs-54-to-rs-22-crore-124020400260_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fparamount-cables-q3-results-net-profit-climbs-54-to-rs-22-crore-124020400260_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ahead%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20Polls%2C%20EC%20Answers%20Longstanding%20Query%20on%20How%20EVMs%20Get%20Signals%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04142329%2FF_r3Z09a8AAxnSm.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20has%20updated%20on%20January%2030%2C%20the%20list%20of%20frequently%20asked%20questions%20(FAQ)%20on%20its%20website%2C%20in%20which%20it%20has%20addressed%20how%20signals%20are%20received%20and%20sent%20between%20the%20EVM%20(electronic%20voting%20machines)%20and%20VVPAT%20(voter%20verified%20paper%20audit%20trails).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20FAQs%20come%20as%20opposition%20parties%20have%20raised%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fjairam-ramesh-evm-concerns-chief-election-commissioner-letter-ec-9091381%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20questions%20about%20the%20role%20of%20EVMs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eci.gov.in%2Fevm-faq-new%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EQuestion%2086%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20FAQs%20answers%20how%20signal%20or%20command%20flow%20between%20various%20units%20of%20EVM%20i.e.%20between%20ballot%20unit%20(BU)%2C%20control%20unit%20(CU)%20and%20VVVPAT.%20It%20also%20answers%20if%20the%20VVPAT%20which%20is%20kept%20along%20with%20BU%20inside%20the%20voting%20compartment%20of%20the%20voter%20receives%20any%20signal%20or%20command%20from%20BU%20and%20vice-versa.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ECI%20has%20stated%20in%20its%20answer%20that%20in%20M3%20EVMs%20(the%20current%20model%20that%20is%20being%20used)%2C%20the%20CU%20acts%20as%20the%20Master%20%E2%80%9Cirrespective%20of%20the%20position%20in%20which%20it%20is%20placed%20or%20connected.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBU%20and%20VVPAT%20act%20as%20Slave%20units%20in%20the%20connected%20network%2C%20which%20receive%20commands%20from%20CU%20to%20act%20as%20per%20the%20application%20programme.%20BU%20and%20VVPAT%20do%20not%20communicate%20with%20each%20other.%20It%20is%20the%20CU%20that%20communicates%20with%20both%20the%20BU%20and%20VVPAT.%20When%20a%20voter%20presses%20a%20candidate%20button%20on%20BU%2C%20the%20BU%20sends%20the%20button%20number%20to%20CU%20and%20in%20turn%2C%20the%20CU%20communicates%20to%20VVPAT%20to%20print%20the%20slip%20of%20the%20corresponding%20button%20number.%20Only%20after%20printing%20and%20cutting%20of%20the%20printed%20VVPAT%20slip%2C%20the%20CU%20registers%20the%20vote%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20website%20shows%20a%20diagram%20to%20explain%20the%20signal%20flow%20details%20int%20he%20M3%20model%20EV-VVPAT.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20states%20that%20in%20the%20M3%20model%2C%E2%80%9DMaster-Slave%20bus%20architecture%20is%20used.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20this%20model%20the%20VVPAT%20can%20be%20connected%20anywhere%20in%20the%20EVM%20M3%20bus.%20The%20Control%20Unit%20(CU)%20implements%20communication%2C%20command%20processing%2C%20handling%20of%20key%20operations%20and%20handling%20of%20all%20the%20commands%2Fresponses%20to%2Ffrom%20BU%20and%20VVPAT.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CCommunication%20on%20the%20bus%20is%20initiated%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9CMaster%E2%80%9D%20(CU)%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9CCommand%E2%80%9D%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9CSlave%E2%80%9D%20(BU%20%26amp%3B%20VVPAT).%20The%20%E2%80%98Slave%E2%80%99%20which%20is%20constantly%20monitoring%20the%20bus%20for%20%E2%80%9CCommands%E2%80%9D%20will%20recognise%20only%20the%20%E2%80%98Commands%E2%80%99%20addressed%20to%20it%20and%20will%20respond%20by%20performing%20an%20action%20and%20by%20returning%20a%20%E2%80%98Response%E2%80%99.%20Only%20the%20Master%20can%20initiate%20a%20command.%20CU%20is%20always%20the%20Master%20in%20the%20ECI%20M3%20EVM%20system%20setup%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20states.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20series%20of%20tweets%20in%202021%2C%20former%20IAS%20officer%20Kannan%20Gopinathan%20raised%20serious%20questions%20over%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Felection-commissions-evms-are-standalone-machines-cant-be-tampered-with-says-expert-committee-2064267.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EECI%E2%80%99s%20claim%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20EVMs%20are%20stand-alone%20machines%20which%20are%20neither%20accessible%20remotely%20from%20any%20network%20nor%20can%20be%20connected%20to%20any%20external%20devices.%20With%20the%20introduction%20of%20VVPAT%2C%20these%20claims%20do%20not%20hold%20as%20these%20machines%20are%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnaukarshah%2Fstatus%2F1360584934159749124%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eapparently%20connected%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20laptops%20or%20symbol%20loading%20units%20(SLUs).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWe%20are%20connecting%20an%20external%20device%20to%20EVM-VVPAT%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ea)%20after%20announcement%20of%20election%20date%3Cbr%3E%5Cnb)%20after%20publication%20of%20candidate%20list%3Cbr%3E%5Cnc)%20after%20both%20stages%20of%20randomisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20more%20stand-alone%2C%20no%20more%20a%20calculator%20%26amp%3B%20none%20of%20the%20process%20safeguards%20are%20effective%20anymore.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FECISVEEP%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40ECISVEEP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Kannan%20Gopinathan%20(%40naukarshah)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnaukarshah%2Fstatus%2F1377225206993887239%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2031%2C%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EVVPATs%20were%20inducted%20into%20the%20electoral%20process%20in%202013%20to%20provide%20an%20additional%20layer%20of%20scrutiny%20against%20possible%20EVM%20manipulation.%20They%20allow%20physical%20tallying%20of%20votes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGopinathan%20said%20that%20with%20the%20addition%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20mechanism%2C%20the%20voting%20process%20became%20%E2%80%9Cvulnerable%20and%20suspicious%E2%80%9D%20instead%20of%20being%20strengthened.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20that%20EVMs%20are%20not%20stand-alone%20machines%20as%20they%20are%20connected%20to%20laptops%20of%20SLUs%20and%20it%20is%20not%20single%20programmable%20as%20they%20are%20showing%20names%20and%20symbols%20of%20candidates.%20%E2%80%9CHow%20do%20you%20store%20it%3F%20You%20need%20a%20programmable%20memory.%20It%20is%20not%20a%20stand%20alone%20machine%20and%20it%20has%20a%20programmable%20memory%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20every%20aspect%20of%20a%20full%20fledged%20computer%20apart%20from%20a%20screen%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Logical%20Indian.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGopinathan%2C%20who%20was%20the%20returning%20officer%20for%20Dadra%20and%20Nagar%20Haveli%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20subsequently%20stepped%20down%20as%20an%20IAS%20officer%20over%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20the%20following%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Felection-commission-of-india-addresses-5-year-old-query-on-electronic-voting-machines-ahead-of-lok-sabha-elections%2Fcid%2F1998185%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Telegraph%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Gopinathan%20said%20that%20while%20he%20has%20not%20examined%20the%20poll%20panel%E2%80%99s%20FAQ%2C%20the%20current%20process%20does%20not%20fulfil%20the%20demands%20of%20a%20fair%20election.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20fair%20election%20is%20one%20where%20the%20voter%20has%20agency%20to%20verify%20the%20vote%2C%20and%20the%20candidate%20can%20verify%20counting.%20The%20current%20process%20fulfills%20neither.%20Verification%20would%20mean%20the%20ability%20to%20accept%20or%20reject%20what%20is%20registered%20on%20the%20VVPAT%20slip%20that%20one%20sees%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Conduct%20of%20Election%20Rules%20say%20that%20in%20case%20of%20a%20mismatch%20between%20the%20CU%20and%20VVPAT%20vote%20tallies%20(five%20are%20tallied%20in%20every%20Assembly%20segment)%2C%20the%20latter%20is%20to%20be%20counted%20for%20that%20machine.%20Thus%2C%20the%20EC%20itself%20considers%20the%20VVPAT%20more%20reliable%20than%20the%20CU.%20Then%20why%20does%20it%20rely%20on%20the%20CU%20count%20for%20the%20overall%20result%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707036852000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04142329%2FF_r3Z09a8AAxnSm.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fevm-election-commission-lok-sabha-faq-signal-kannan-gopinathan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%202021%20former%20IAS%20officer%20Kannan%20Gopinathan%20raised%20serious%20questions%20over%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20claim%20that%20EVMs%20are%20stand-alone%20machines%20which%20are%20neither%20accessible%20remotely%20from%20any%20network%20nor%20can%20be%20connected%20to%20any%20external%20devices%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fevm-election-commission-lok-sabha-faq-signal-kannan-gopinathan%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Union%20Home%20Ministry%20Cancels%20Christian%20Organisation's%20FCRA%20Licence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F24214119%2Fmha.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20long%20list%20of%20cancellations%2C%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20on%20February%203%2C%20cancelled%20the%20Foreign%20Contribution%20Regulation%20Act%20(FCRA)%20registration%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Social%20Service%20Society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20society%2C%20abbreviated%20as%20TNSOSS%2C%20is%20a%20Christian%20non-governmental%20organisation%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Catholic%20Bishops%20Conference.%20The%20Union%20government%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20TNSOSS%20had%20violated%20FCRA%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20Tamil%20Nadu-based%20Christian%20association%20the%20FCRA%20registration%20of%20which%20has%20been%20cancelled%20in%202024%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftamil-nadu-social-service-organisation-loses-fcra-registration%2Farticle67808370.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20The%20other%20one%20was%20the%20World%20Vision%20India%2C%20which%20lost%20its%20licence%20on%20January%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20before%20that%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20also%20cancelled%20the%20licence%20of%20the%20New%20Delhi-based%20Centre%20for%20Policy%20Research%20(CPR)%2C%20a%20public%20policy%20think%20tank.%20The%20president%20of%20the%20organisation%20Yamini%20Aiyar%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhome-ministry-cancels-centre-for-policy-researchs-fcra-registration%5C%22%3Ecalled%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20basis%20of%20this%20decision%20%E2%80%9Cincomprehensible%20and%20disproportionate%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20a%20series%20of%20amendments%20to%20the%20FCRA%2C%20successive%20governments%20had%20imposed%20restrictions%20on%20the%20activities%20of%20several%20NGOs%2C%20leading%20them%20to%20face%20several%20challenges%20including%20a%20loss%20of%20jobs.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20concerns%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20using%20the%20FCRA%20to%20curb%20the%20activities%20of%20NGOs%20that%20are%20critical%20of%20it%20have%20been%20raised%20in%20the%20back%20of%20thousands%20of%20licence%20cancellations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftamil-nadu-social-service-organisation-loses-fcra-registration%2Farticle67808370.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%20that%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%20since%202011%2C%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20has%20cancelled%20more%20than%2020%2C000%20NGOs%E2%80%99%20registrations%2C%20citing%20violations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707036382000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F24214119%2Fmha.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Funion-home-ministry-cancels-christian-organisations-fcra-licence%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20is%20the%20second%20Tamil%20Nadu-based%20Christian%20association%20the%20FCRA%20registration%20of%20which%20has%20been%20cancelled%20in%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Funion-home-ministry-cancels-christian-organisations-fcra-licence%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Reggae%20icon%20Aston%20'Family%20Man'%20Barrett%2C%20Bob%20Marley's%20bassist%2C%20dies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707035736000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F17E98%2Fproduction%2F_132544979_mediaitem132544978.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68196823%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aston%20Barrett%2C%20bassist%20for%20Bob%20Marley%20and%20the%20Wailers%2C%20was%20a%20key%20player%20in%20the%20growth%20of%20reggae.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A927%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68196823%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68196823.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68196823.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IBBI%20allows%20same%20RP%20for%20company%20and%20personal%20guarantor%20insolvency%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707034970000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-01%2F11%2Ffull%2F1673457901-0622.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanie