0in%20a%20series%20of%20such%20demonstrations%20across%20Germany.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FzUNrvEqrCf%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FzUNrvEqrCf%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FfskmumkJWn%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FfskmumkJWn%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20DW%20News%20(%40dwnews)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdwnews%2Fstatus%2F1753823771574550920%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%203%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELargest%20protest%20since%20mid-January%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudging%20by%20official%20police%20estimates%2C%20Saturday%E2%80%99s%20rally%20in%20Berlin%20was%20the%20largest%20protest%20since%20mid-January%2C%20when%20nationwide%20protests%20kicked%20off%20a%20wave%20of%20rallies%20against%20the%20far%20right.%20These%20demonstrations%20began%20after%20a%20report%20published%20by%20media%20outlet%20Correctiv%20on%20January%2010%20revealed%20that%20party%20members%20of%20the%20Alternative%20for%20Germany%20(AfD)had%20met%20right-wing%20extremists%2C%20some%20Christian%20Democrats%20(CDU)%20and%20business%20people%20in%20November%202023%20to%20discuss%20plans%20for%20mass%20deportations%20from%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20millions%20of%20Germans%20have%20taken%20a%20stand%20against%20right-wing%20extremism.%20The%20number%20of%20organizations%20calling%20for%20Berliners%20to%20protest%20has%20grown%20to%20well%20over%201%2C800.%20Among%20them%20are%20prominent%20civil%20society%20associations%2C%20including%20all%20major%20charities%20and%20many%20committed%20albeit%20little%20known%20activists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20two%20dozen%20speakers%20addressed%20the%20Berlin%20crowd%20on%20Saturday%2C%20many%20of%20them%20younger%20than%2040.%20One%20of%20the%20better-known%20speakers%20was%20Luisa%20Neubauer%2C%20of%20the%20Fridays%20for%20Future%20climate%20protests.%20She%20hoped%20Saturday%E2%80%99s%20rally%20would%20give%20rise%20to%20a%20broad%20social%20movement%20to%20counter%20right-wing%20extremism%20and%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHope%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20fall%20from%20the%20sky.%20Hope%20is%20damn%20hard%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20Neubauer%20told%20protesters.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20democracy.%20You%20live%20democracy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtesters%20were%20seen%20brandishing%20a%20host%20of%20homemade%20placards%20with%20witty%20slogans%20%E2%80%94%20many%20of%20which%20were%20directed%20at%20the%20right-wing%20populist%20AfD.%20Calls%20for%20more%20social%20work%2C%20better%20education%20and%20for%20strengthening%20initiatives%20to%20tackle%20right-wing%20extremism%20drew%20applause%20from%20everyone%2C%20whereas%20slogans%20directed%20against%20the%20incumbent%20three-party%20coalition%20and%20opposition%20CDU%2FCSU%20parties%20were%20not%20well%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeakers%20from%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20eastern%20states%20of%20Brandenburg%2C%20Thuringia%20and%20Saxony%20received%20particular%20applause%20and%20cheers.%20They%20described%20living%20in%20fear%2C%20being%20harassed%20and%20subjected%20to%20violence%20by%20the%20far%20right%20%E2%80%94%20but%20also%20lauded%20a%20new%20awareness%20among%20civil%20society%20actors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSending%20greetings%20of%20solidarity%20to%20all%20those%20taking%20to%20the%20streets%20in%20Dresden%20and%20Glauchau%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%2021-year-old%20student%20and%20author%20Jakob%20Springfeld%20told%20the%20crowd.%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20where%20it%20counts.%E2%80%9D%20Both%20cities%20are%20home%20to%20right-wing%20extremist%20milieus.%20Most%20protesters%20paid%20close%20attention%20to%20speeches%20like%20these%2C%20including%20to%20reports%20detailing%20growing%20pressure%20from%20right-wing%20extremists%20and%20acts%20of%20violence%20against%20journalists%2C%20including%20the%20Correctiv%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Freedom%2C%20democracy%2C%20plurality%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaturday%E2%80%99s%20colourful%20crowd%20included%20many%20families%2C%20some%20of%20them%20spanning%20three%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20my%20children%20to%20learn%20what%20democracy%20and%20participating%20in%20public%20life%20means%20from%20an%20early%20age%2C%20and%20how%20to%20stand%20up%20for%20their%20rights%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20mother%20of%20two%20small%20children%20from%20Berlin%E2%80%99s%20Wedding%20district%20told%20DW.%20An%20older%20lady%20told%20DW%20she%20had%20come%20to%20the%20rally%20because%20of%20%E2%80%9Cfreedom%2C%20democracy%2C%20plurality%2C%20and%20to%20keep%20Berlin%20like%20Berlin.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJannis%2C%20a%20teacher%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20give%20his%20last%20name%2C%20attended%20the%20protest%20with%20a%20group%20of%20people%20from%20South%20Korea%2C%20Vietnam%20and%20China.%20His%20held%20a%20sign%20reading%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20Germany%2C%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%9CGermany%20is%20us%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20back.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20as%20a%20community%20of%20Asians%20want%20to%20show%20that%20we%20also%20belong%20to%20Germany%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20DW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20take%20a%20stand%20against%20the%20right%2C%20it%20shows%20how%20much%20we%20belong%20to%20this%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%20Jannis%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20China%2C%20told%20DW%20he%20has%20been%20living%20in%20Germany%20for%2020%20years%2C%20working%20and%20paying%20taxes.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20yet%20I%20always%20have%20the%20feeling%20that%20I%20have%20to%20go%20the%20extra%20mile%2C%20that%20I%20always%20need%20to%20prove%20I%20belong.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20colleagues%20could%20be%20seen%20holding%20a%20cardboard%20sign%20reading%3A%20%E2%80%9CSkilled%20workers%20from%20abroad%3F%20Openness%20and%20diversity%20are%20the%20prerequisites.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMore%20protests%20planned%20for%20Sunday%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Berlin%20rally%20was%20the%20largest%20such%20protest%20in%20Germany%20on%20Saturday%2C%20it%20was%20by%20no%20means%20the%20only%20one.%20And%20more%20protests%20are%20set%20to%20follow%20on%20Sunday.%20Special%20attention%20is%20also%20being%20paid%20to%20eastern%20Germany%2C%20where%20smaller%20towns%20will%20see%20some%20of%20largest%20protest%20since%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20Berlin%20Wall%20in%201989.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToward%20the%20end%20of%20Saturday%E2%80%99s%20rally%20in%20Berlin%2C%20one%20final%20speaker%20told%20attendees%20that%20another%20large%20protest%20is%20due%20to%20be%20held%20in%20the%20same%20location%20on%20June%208%20%E2%80%94%20the%20day%20before%20the%20European%20Parliament%20elections%20in%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20report%20first%20appeared%20on%20DW.%20Read%20the%20original%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fthousands-crowd-central-berlin-to-protest-far-right%2Fa-68166547%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707027713000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04114952%2FGFbjYInXAAEvZzw.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fon-rainy-weekend-thousands-crowd-berlin-to-protest-against-the-far-right%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22More%20than%20150%2C000%20protesters%20gathered%20in%20the%20German%20capital%20on%20Saturday%20to%20take%20a%20stand%20against%20right-wing%20extremism.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fon-rainy-weekend-thousands-crowd-berlin-to-protest-against-the-far-right%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ayo%20Edebiri%20Acknowledges%20Making%20Fun%20of%20Jennifer%20Lopez%20in%20%E2%80%98SNL%E2%80%99%20Sketch%3A%20%E2%80%98It%E2%80%99s%20Wrong%20to%20Run%20Yo