%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fsnl-ayo-edebiri-nikki-haley-slavery-civil-war-1235896679%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fsnl-ayo-edebiri-nikki-haley-slavery-civil-war-1235896679%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Not%20Mumbai%2C%20This%20City%20Has%20The%20Worst%20Traffic%20Congestion%20In%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20capital%20London%20was%20the%20slowest%20city%20to%20drive%20through%202023%20in%20the%20world%2C%20with%20an%20average%20speed%20of%2014%20kmph%20in%20rush%20hour%2C%20a%20report%20said.%20Two%20Indian%20cities%2C%20Bengaluru%20and%20Pune%2C%20were%20also%20on%20the%20list%20of%20cities%20with%20the%20worst%20traffic%2C%20the%20report%20by%20the%20Amsterdam-based%20location%20technology%20specialist%20TomTom%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tomtom.com%2Ftraffic-index%2Franking%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETomTom%20Traffic%20Index%3C%2Fa%3E%20evaluated%20387%20cities%20across%2055%20countries%20on%20six%20continents%20by%20their%20average%20travel%20time%2C%20fuel%20costs%2C%20and%20CO2%20emissions.%20It%20was%20based%20on%20data%20from%20over%20600%20million%20in-car%20navigation%20systems%20and%20smartphones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20each%20city%2C%20TomTom%20calculated%20the%20average%20travel%20time%20per%20kilometer%20from%20the%20time%20it%20took%20to%20cover%20the%20millions%20of%20kilometers%20driven%20across%20the%20entire%20network%20in%20the%20year%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBengaluru%2C%20Pune%20Among%20Cities%20With%20Worst%20Traffic%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengaluru%20(6)%20and%20Pune%20(7)%20were%20the%20two%20Indian%20cities%20that%20were%20named%20among%20the%20world's%20ten%20worst%20traffic-hit%20cities%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20average%20travel%20time%20per%2010%20km%20in%202023%20was%2028%20minutes%2010%20seconds%2C%20while%20in%20Pune%2C%20it%20was%2027%20minutes%2050%20seconds%2C%20the%20TomTom%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengaluru%2C%20the%20IT%20capital%20of%20India%2C%20was%20also%20named%20the%20second%20most%20congested%20city%20in%202023%20after%20Ireland's%20capital%20Dublin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20worst%20day%20to%20travel%20through%20Bengaluru%20last%20year%20was%20September%2027%2C%20when%20the%20average%20travel%20time%20to%20drive%2010%20km%20was%20recorded%20at%2032%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Pune%2C%20which%20was%20the%20sixth%20most%20congested%20city%20last%20year%2C%C2%A0it%20was%20September%208%2C%20when%20it%20took%20about%2034%20minutes%20to%20cover%20a%20distance%20of%2010%20km.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDelhi%2C%20Mumbai%20Also%20Hit%20By%20Traffic%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20(44)%20and%20Mumbai%20(52)%20were%20also%20on%20the%20TomTom%20Traffic%20Index.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Delhi%2C%20on%20average%2C%20it%20took%2021%20minutes%2040%20seconds%20to%20drive%2010%20km%20in%202023%2C%20and%2021%20minutes%2020%20seconds%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20report%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ELondon%2C%20Dublin%2C%20Toronto%20Worst%20Traffic-Hit%20Cities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELondon%2C%20with%20an%20average%20travel%20time%20per%2010%20km%20of%2037%20minutes%2C%20was%20the%20city%20worst%20affected%20by%20traffic%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20the%20TomTom%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDublin%20had%20an%20average%20travel%20time%20per%2010%20km%20of%2029%20minutes%2030%20seconds%20last%20year%20and%20was%20ranked%20second%20on%20the%20list%2C%20while%20Toronto%20in%20Canada%2C%C2%A0where%20it%20took%2029%20minutes%20to%20travel%2010%20km%2C%20was%20named%20third.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20London%20and%20Dublin%2C%20travel%20times%20for%20around%20a%209-km%20journey%20increased%20by%20%2B1%20minute%20compared%20to%202022%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAverage%20Speed%20Decreased%20In%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20the%20average%20speed%20decreased%20in%20228%20of%20the%20387%20cities%20analyzed%20in%20the%20traffic%20index%2C%20compared%20to%202022%2C%20TomTom%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%2082%20cities%20saw%20their%20average%20speed%20remain%20unchanged%2C%20while%2077%20cities%20had%20a%20higher%20average%20speed%20and%20shorter%20journey%20times%20than%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20more%20than%2060%25%20of%20351%20cities%20where%20TomTom%20aggregated%20fuel%20prices%2C%20the%20average%20budget%20in%20fuel%20increased%20by%2015%25%20or%20more%20between%202021%20and%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707021600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fa5jve578_traffic-generic_625x300_04_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftraffic-tomtom-traffic-index-this-city-has-the-worst-traffic-congestion-in-india-ranks-2nd-globally-4990411%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20UK%20capital%20London%20was%20the%20slowest%20city%20to%20drive%20through%202023%2C%20with%20an%20average%20speed%20of%2014%20kmph%20in%20rush%20hour%2C%20a%20report%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftraffic-tomtom-traffic-index-this-city-has-the-worst-traffic-congestion-in-india-ranks-2nd-globally-4990411%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftraffic-tomtom-traffic-index-this-city-has-the-worst-traffic-congestion-in-india-ranks-2nd-globally-4990411%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftraffic-tomtom-traffic-index-this-city-has-the-worst-traffic-congestion-in-india-ranks-2nd-globally-4990411%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20NI%20confirms%20first%20nationalist%20leader%2C%20is%20a%20united%20Ireland%20within%20'touching%20distance'%3F%20%7C%20Adam%20Boulton%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publish