ivor%20and%20a%20psychologist%2C%20I%20know%20how%20taking%20medicine%20can%20feel%20like%20a%20way%20out.%20However%2C%20I%20sincerely%20believe%20in%20trying%20everything%20in%20my%20power%20before%20referring%20patients%20to%20a%20psychiatrist.%20We%20believe%20in%20creating%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20the%20trauma%20survivor%20and%20helping%20them%20heal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20how%20healing%20is%20not%20linear%2C%20she%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CEven%20though%20I%20am%20an%20adult%20out%20of%20that%20house%20and%20all%20the%20trauma%20it%20brought%2C%20I%20still%20get%20stuck%20in%20toxic%20cycles.%20I%20am%20happy%20that%20I%20am%20away%20from%20it%2C%20but%20I%20still%20believe%20that%20healing%20is%20not%20linear%20and%20you%20can%20always%20slip%20back.%20I%20still%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20isolate%20myself%20and%20disassociate%20from%20my%20body.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC1Ujj20yvra%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC1Ujj20yvra%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22