ell%20from%20Rs%202%2C72%2C707%20to%20Rs%201%2C67%2C001%20for%20the%20same%20period%20%E2%80%94%20a%2040%25%20fall.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20quantity%20of%20water%20supplied%20per%20day%20increased%20from%201.65%20lakh%20litres%20to%202.09%20lakh%20litres%20%E2%80%94%20additional%20supply%20of%2044%2C180%20litres.%20These%20savings%20can%20be%20used%20for%20providing%20other%20amenities%20to%20the%20public.%20The%20results%20for%20Ponmudi%20have%20been%20reflected%20in%20other%20villages%20too.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Renuva%20Devi%2C%20Panchayat%20president%20of%20Kuttapalayam%20village%20also%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20we%20are%20not%20dependent%20on%20the%20tank%20operator.%20Water%20is%20automatically%20supplied%20to%20the%20public%20at%20pre-set%20timings.%20There%20have%20hardly%20been%20any%20complaints%20regarding%20water%20supply%20from%20the%20public.%20Fixed%20quantity%20is%20being%20supplied%20for%20a%20fixed%20timing%20and%20then%2C%20there%20are%20water%20savings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20systems%20also%20helped%20alleviate%20the%20burden%20on%20women%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20from%20households%20with%20no%20direct%20water%20supply%20connections%20who%20often%20spend%20a%20long%20time%20waiting%20near%20taps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20society%2C%20the%20burden%20of%20fetching%20water%20falls%20on%20women.%20Water%20is%20supplied%20through%20household%20connections%20or%20public%20fountains%20in%20rural%20areas.%20Those%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20these%20connections%20or%20who%20are%20not%20getting%20adequate%20quantities%20of%20water%20through%20such%20connections%20were%20either%20forced%20to%20purchase%20water%20in%20the%20private%20market%20or%20wait%20at%20public%20fountains.%20The%20burden%20on%20women%20was%20further%20aggravated%20because%20of%20unreliable%20water%20supply%20timings.%20They%20would%20have%20to%20wait%20at%20odd%20timings%20and%20for%20long%20periods%20for%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20informs%20DC%20Sunkara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9COut%20of%204%2C18%2C981%20households%2C%203%2C56%2C101%20have%20connections%20under%20the%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%2C%20and%20works%20are%20ongoing%20for%20giving%20functional%20household%20tap%20connections%20to%20all.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIAS-Erode-Water-Supply-1706794104.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Villages%20in%20Erode%20district%20are%20now%20benefitting%20from%20timely%20water%20supply.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIAS-Erode-Water-Supply-1706794104.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIAS-Erode-Water-Supply-1706794104-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIAS-Erode-Water-Supply-1706794104-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIAS-Erode-Water-Supply-1706794104-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIAS-Erode-Water-Supply-1706794104-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340530%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVillages%20in%20Erode%20district%20are%20now%20benefitting%20from%20timely%20water%20supply.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKalaiselvi%2C%20a%2032-year-old%20resident%20of%20Ponmudi%20village%2C%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20water%20supply%20in%20our%20village%20was%20problematic.%20It%20was%20managed%20by%20a%20waterman%20(tank%20operator).%20He%20would%20switch%20on%20the%20motor%20pump%20to%20the%20overhead%20tanks%20and%20forget%20to%20switch%20it%20off.%20We%20would%20have%20to%20call%20and%20remind%20him%2C%20and%20only%20then%20would%20he%20switch%20off%20the%20motor.%20There%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20water%20wastage%20due%20to%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDespite%20tap%20connections%20being%20affected%20to%20all%20households%20under%20the%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%2C%20we%20never%20knew%20when%20water%20would%20be%20supplied.%20Most%20of%20the%20women%20in%20the%20village%20go%20to%20work.%20On%20days%20when%20water%20is%20supplied%2C%20they%20would%20have%20to%20take%20leave%20or%20not%20be%20able%20to%20fetch%20water.%20Moreover%2C%20houses%20at%20a%20higher%20elevation%20used%20to%20get%20less%20water%20and%20those%20at%20a%20lower%20elevation%20used%20to%20get%20more%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20a%20fixed%20quantity%20of%20water%20is%20being%20supplied%20at%20pre-set%20timings%2C%20irrespective%20of%20elevation.%20Today%2C%20our%20area%20gets%20water%20from%206%20am%20to%208%20am%20every%20day.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F303367%2Fbengaluru-women-teach-how-to-compost-grow-vegetables-at-home-using-whatsapp-group-urban-gardening%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhatsApp%20group%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20created%20in%20which%20water%20supply%20timings%20are%20informed%20to%20us.%20Water%20wastage%20and%20electricity%20bills%20also%20have%20come%20down.%20We%20are%20not%20forced%20to%20take%20leave%20%5Bfrom%20work%5D%20for%20fetching%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kalaiselvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20forward%2C%20the%20plan%20is%20to%20install%20these%20IoT%20devices%20in%20OHTs%20located%20in%20other%20villages%20too.%20%E2%80%9COur%20vision%20is%20to%20harness%20available%20technology%20and%20expand%20this%20initiative%2C%20one%20village%20at%20a%20time%2C%20utilising%20existing%20funds%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20DC%20Sunkara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20%